We love this memory, Joe! We look forward to creating more memories with you for the year's to come! -Bri

Hey, Rick. We apologize if you had a less than comfortable boarding experience in Nashville today. Creating a safe environment in the terminal and inflight is important to us, and we appreciate you sharing this feedback and concern with us directly. -Rachel

Hi, Yvan. I apologize for the delay in response, especially if you reached out multiple times with us. That said, I'm happy to help assist you today. Please DM us your confirmation number so we can take a further look. -Bri

Sorry that our Team wasn't able to fulfill your requests, Sabrina. The last thing we ever want to do is leave a sour taste in your mouth, but we must maintain the integrity of our policies. Please reach out to our Group Reservations Team directly at 800-433-5368. -Austin
